name: Aether
description:
You may not be there for my five senses,
my eyes may not be able to see you,
my ears may not hear your euphonious voice,
my nose may not get your sweet bodily smell,
my tongue may forget the taste of your love,
my skin may yearn for the touch,

but here you are! Immortalised,
my wanderlust girl in the Blockchain World.
